ent on to study at brentwood academy where she received a level two and level three diploma in beauty specialised techniques before working as a therapist in harmony health and beauty at epping forest country club for two years childs became well known in  while appearing in the itv semireality programme the only way is essex childs later signed to can associates management agency the same agency that represented jordan childs’s heroine childs puts her name to a ghostwritten column for new continue reading » angela griffin angela is a popular british actress and television presenter who has been a mainstay on british television since the early s she appeared in the popular longrunning british soap operas emmerdale and most famously in coronation street as fiona middleton from  to  subsequently she joined the bbc medical drama series holby city as staff nurse jasmine hopkins she has also appeared in the bbc dramas cutting it and down to earth from  to  she appeared as teacher kim campbell in the bbc school drama series waterloo road angela is also an established presenter and in january  she copresented sky ’s coverage of the golden globes red carpet alongside gethin jones she also presented the midweek national lottery in  and also took part in the bbc’s millennium programme on new year’s eve in  she presented a programme on the uk’s channel  on the subject of mixed race people continue reading » page  of end » please also visit we were delighted to have worked with you and pollyanna woodward more thanks for arranging pierluigi collina to work with mars foods ltd onmore without your involvement the tvc with steffi graf for sure deodorant wmore we will definitely be using your fantastic service georgie bradshaw �more it was such a pleasure working with you sylvia palamoundian – accounmore we were so pleased that you managed to arrange bill bailey for us on bmore thanks for taking the trouble to visit us to discuss the project pippamore we hope you will accept this fo