ilence on his love child with anna eberstein i love him very much us weekly the actor is also a dad to two other kids daughter tabitha  and son felix  months with tinglan hong   nu kan anna från sundsvall fira ny babylycka med hugh grant  now anna from sundsvall celebrates new baby happiness with hugh grant sundsvalls tidning  december  retrieved  december  anna ebersteins mamma susanne eberstein socialdemokratisk riksdagsledamot som bor i sundsvall bekräftar att de fått ytterligare ett barn  anna ebersteins mother susanne eberstein a social democratic member of parliament who lives in sundsvall confirmed that they had another child   emma griffiths hugh grant reverts to type to charm lib dems archived  january  at the wayback machine bbc news  september   hugh grant backing danny alexander in election the scotsman  april  retrieved  may    lindsay caron  may  fancy a chance of dinner with hugh grant just donate to lib dems before monday evening liberal democrat voice retrieved  may    a b c tom watson should be prime minister says hugh grant archived  march  at the wayback machine express  star  may   katy forrester hugh grant jokes about seeing his former agent in the bath in hilarious video for labour mp candidate archived  march  at the wayback machine mirror  april   mcleod keith  may  grants uefa cup final ticket search daily record scotland glasgow retrieved  march    up close and personal variety  december  pp a–  accessdate requires url help  hugh grant biography net worth quotes wiki assets cars homes and more born rich retrieved  october    bbc apologises for hugh grant’s gay rugby comment pink news  march  retrieved  march    amanda williams docs honoured in uk health awards archived  march  at the wayback machine  may  oxford mail  hugh grant backs bipolar disorder experience website archived  march  at the wayback machine equilibrium the bipolar foundation  january   fiona barr patient experience pioneer dies digitalhealthnet  may   actor hugh grant drops into faversham to support fynvola foundation archived  march  at the wayback machine kent online  june   hugh grant backs marie curie cancer care appeal in his mothers memory archived  january  at the wayback machine telegraph  february   hugh grant backs wiltshire daffodil appeal archived  march  at the wayback machine gazette  herald  february   hugh grant in video plea for marie curie fund bolton news  march   mary elizabeth williams pancreatic cancer action charity should realise that the disease is not a competition archived  march  at the wayback machine independent  february   hugh grant holds a purple p to show his support for pancreatic cancer awareness month archived  april  at the wayback machine press release pancreatic cancer action  november  external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to hugh grant hugh grant on imdb hugh grant at allmovie hugh grant at box office mojo hugh grant at the british film institutes screenonline hugh grant on charlie rose hugh grant collected news and commentary the guardian  hugh grant collected news and commentary the new york times  and in nyt movies hugh grant interview on bbc radio  desert island discs april   hugh grant interview at museum of the moving image about florence foster jenkins v t e – news corporation scandal events news international phone hacking scandal news of the world royal phone hacking scandal news corporation takeover bid for bskyb news of the world phone hacking scandal investigations closure of the news of the world companies and organisations news corporation news international news of the world the sun the times the sunday times news limited other bskyb culture media and sport committee federal bureau of investigation harbottle  lewis independent police complaints commission metropolitan police role ofcom press complaints commission serious fraud office solicitors regulation authority people known victims  attack victims leslie ash gordon brown lee chapman charlotte church steve