tte davis  jean delannoy  rené ferracci  claude lanzmann  jeanluc godard  serge silberman  bernard blier  paul grimault  gérard philipe  jeanpierre aumont  sophia loren  michèle morgan  sylvester stallone  jean marais  marcello mastroianni  gérard oury  jean carmet  jeanne moreau  gregory peck  steven spielberg  lauren bacall  henri verneuil  charles aznavour  andie macdowell  michael douglas  clint eastwood  jeanluc godard  pedro almodóvar  johnny depp  jean rochefort  josiane balasko  georges cravenne  jeanpierre léaud  martin scorsese  –present darry cowl  charlotte rampling  agnès varda  anouk aimée  jeremy irons  claude rich  bernadette lafont  spike lee  meryl streep  micheline presle  jacques dutronc  will smith  hugh grant  pierre richard  marlène jobert  jude law  jeanne moreau  roberto benigni  dustin hoffman  harrison ford  quentin tarantino  kate winslet  kevin costner  scarlett johansson  sean penn  michael douglas  george clooney  v t e london film critics circle award for british actor of the year alan rickman  daniel daylewis  david thewlis  ralph fiennes  nigel hawthorne  ewan mcgregor  ian mckellen  robert carlyle  brendan gleeson  jeremy northam  jim broadbent  paul bettany  hugh grant  paul bettany  daniel craig  ralph fiennes  toby jones  james mcavoy  michael fassbender  colin firth  christian bale  michael fassbender  toby jones  james mcavoy  timothy spall  tom hardy  andrew garfield  v t e volpi cup for best actor – wallace beery  pierre blanchar  paul muni  emil jannings  leslie howard  ermete zacconi  fosco giachetti  pierre fresnay  ernst deutsch  joseph cotten  sam jaffe  jean gabin  fredric march  henri vilbert  jean gabin  curd jürgenskenneth more  bourvil  anthony franciosa  alec guinness  james stewart  john mills  toshiro mifune  burt lancaster  albert finney  tom courtenay  toshiro mifune  jacques perrin  ljubiša samardžić  john marley  – guy boydgeorge dzundzadavid alan griermitchell lichtensteinmatthew modinemichael wright  naseeruddin shah  gérard depardieu  carlo delle piane  hugh grantjames wilby  don amechejoe mantegna  marcello mastroiannimassimo troisi  oleg borisov  river phoenix  jack lemmon  fabrizio bentivogliomarcello mastroianni  xia yuroberto citran  götz georgeian hart  liam neesonchris penn  wesley snipes  sean penn  jim broadbent  javier bardem  –present luigi lo cascio  stefano accorsi  sean penn  javier bardem  david strathairn  ben affleck  brad pitt  silvio orlando  colin firth  vincent gallo  michael fassbender  philip seymour hoffmanjoaquin phoenix  themis panou  adam driver  fabrice luchini  oscar martínez  authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn no isni    x gnd  sudoc  bnf cb data musicbrainz cefadcabdadaee ndl  bne xx retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlehughgrantoldid categories  birthsthcentury english male actorsstcentury english male actorsalumni of new college oxfordbafta winners peoplebest actor bafta award winnersbest british actor empire award winnersbest musical or comedy actor golden globe film winnerscésar award winnersenglish film producersenglish male film actorsenglish male television actorsactors at the royal exchange manchesterenglish people of scottish descentliving peoplepeople associated with the news international phone hacking scandalpeople educated at latymer upper schoolpeople from chiswickpeople from hammersmithvolpi cup winnershidden categories pages using citations with accessdate and no urlwebarchive template wayback linkspages with citations having bare urlscs errors datesuse british english from april use dmy dates from april articles with hcardswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifierswikipedia articles with bnf identifierswikipedia articles with musicbrainz identifiersgood articles navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants view