ard depardieu  robin williams  tim robbins  robin williams  hugh grant  john travolta  tom cruise  jack nicholson  michael caine  jim carrey  george clooney  –present gene hackman  richard gere  bill murray  jamie foxx  joaquin phoenix  sacha baron cohen  johnny depp  colin farrell  robert downey jr  paul giamatti  jean dujardin  hugh jackman  leonardo dicaprio  michael keaton  matt damon  ryan gosling  v t e honorary césar – ingrid bergman  diana ross  henri langlois  jacques tati  robert dorfmann  rené goscinny  marcel carné  charles vanel  walt disney  pierre braunberger  louis de funès  kirk douglas  marcel pagnol  alain resnais  georges dancigers  alexandre mnouchkine  jean nény  andrzej wajda  raimu  rené clément  georges de beauregard  edwige feuillère  christianjaque  danielle darrieux  christine gouzerénal  alain poiré  maurice jarre  bette davis  jean delannoy  rené ferracci  claude lanzmann  jeanluc godard  serge silberman  bernard blier  paul grimault  gérard philipe  jeanpierre aumont  sophia loren  michèle morgan  sylvester stallone  jean marais  marcello mastroianni  gérard oury  jean carmet  jeanne moreau  gregory peck  steven spielberg  lauren bacall  henri verneuil  charles aznavour  andie macdowell  michael douglas  clint eastwood  jeanluc godard  pedro almodóvar  johnny depp  jean rochefort  josiane balasko  georges cravenne  jeanpierre léaud  martin scorsese  –present darry cowl  charlotte rampling  agnès varda  anouk aimée  jeremy irons  claude rich  bernadette lafont  spike lee  meryl streep  micheline presle  jacques dutronc  will smith  hugh grant  pierre richard  marlène jobert  jude law  jeanne moreau  roberto benigni  dustin hoffman  harrison ford  quentin tarantino  kate winslet  kevin costner  scarlett johansson  sean penn  michael douglas  george clooney  v t e london film critics circle award for british actor of the year alan rickman  daniel daylewis  david thewlis  ralph fiennes  nigel hawthorne  ewan mcgregor  ian mckellen  robert 