il  anthony franciosa  alec guinness  james stewart  john mills  toshiro mifune  burt lancaster  albert finney  tom courtenay  toshiro mifune  jacques perrin  ljubiša samardžić  john marley  – guy boydgeorge dzundzadavid alan griermitchell lichtensteinmatthew modinemichael wright  naseeruddin shah  gérard depardieu  carlo delle piane  hugh grantjames wilby  don amechejoe mantegna  marcello mastroiannimassimo troisi  oleg borisov  river phoenix  jack lemmon  fabrizio bentivogliomarcello mastroianni  xia yuroberto citran  götz georgeian hart  liam neesonchris penn  wesley snipes  sean penn  jim broadbent  javier bardem  –present luigi lo cascio  stefano accorsi  sean penn  javier bardem  david strathairn  ben affleck  brad pitt  silvio orlando  colin firth  vincent gallo  michael fassbender  philip seymour hoffmanjoaquin phoenix  themis panou  adam driver  fabrice luchini  oscar martínez  authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn no isni    x gnd  sudoc  bnf cb data musicbrainz cefadcabdadaee ndl  bne xx retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlehughgrantoldid categories  birthsthcentury english male actorsstcentury english male actorsalumni of new college oxfordbafta winners peoplebest actor bafta award winnersbest british actor empire award winnersbest musical or comedy actor golden globe film winnerscésar award winnersenglish film producersenglish male film actorsenglish male television actorsactors at the royal exchange manchesterenglish people of scottish descentliving peoplepeople associated with the news international phone hacking scandalpeople educated at latymer upper schoolpeople from chiswickpeople from hammersmithvolpi cup winnershidden categories pages using citations with accessdate and no urlwebarchive template wayback linkspages with citations having bare urlscs errors datesuse british english from april use dmy dates from april articles with hcardswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia a