iew ibm lectureship in business and finance hjalma johnson green lecture speeches hugh grant hugh grant chairman president  ceo monsanto company hugh grant is chairman of the board president and chief executive officer of monsanto company monsanto is an agriculture company focused on applying innovation and technology to make its farmer customers more productive and profitable by offering products that help farmers produce food fiber and feed today monsanto has platforms in largeacre crops including corn cotton and oilseeds as well as smallacre crops including its seminis vegetableseed business monsantos established brands  including dekalb asgrow and stoneville seed  and its biotechnology products  including roundup ready soybeans corn and cotton bollgard insectprotected cotton and the yieldgard family of insectprotected corn  have established monsanto as a leader in the agricultural seedandtrait industry additionally roundup agricultural herbicides remain the worlds no  selling herbicides in addition to these core businesses mr grant is also responsible for the strategic planning and development of new growth platforms from monsantos researchanddevelopment investments in genomics biotechnology and other technologies applied to agricultural food and animal production systems prior to his appointment as president and ceo of monsanto in may  and chairman of the board in october  mr grant served three years as executive vice president and chief operating officer with overall responsibility for leading the operations and performance of the commercial seed chemistry and biotechnology traits businesses inclusive of sales and marketing information technology distribution and manufacturing worldwide mr grant joined the former monsanto company in  in scotland and spent the first  years of his career with monsantos agricultural business in a variety of european sales product development and management responsibilities in  he relocated to st louis as global strategy director of the agriculture division and was responsible for global management of the roundup herbicide franchise in  he was named monsantos managing director for the asiapacific region where he had responsibility for the companys agriculture nutrition and pharmaceutical businesses in southeast asia in  mr grant was named copresident of the companys agriculture division where he jointly oversaw global business operations and led the business and product strategy in this role he also formulated the longterm business strategy that led to an integrated product portfolio platform of chemistry seeds and biotechnology traits mr grant is a director of ppg industries inc and is a board member of the donald danforth plant science center and the biotechnology industry organization bio he is a member of the presidents advisory group of croplife international and a member of civic progress in st louis mr grant serves on the board of trustees of washington university and is an international advisory board member of scottish enterprise born in larkhall scotland mr grant earned a bachelors of science degree in agricultural zoology with honors at glasgow university he also earned a postgraduate degree in agriculture at edinburgh university and a masters of business administration at the international management centre in buckingham united kingdom monsanto company nyse mon is a leading global provider of technologybased solutions and agricultural products that improve farm productivity and food quality for more information on monsanto see wwwmonsantocom  request info  visit us  apply westminster college  westminster ave fulton mo  wcmo   email westminster quick links   about us who we are facts history outcomes student life campus map careers academics majors and minors signature programs registrar library catalog facultystaff directory bookstore admissions why westminster request info schedule a visit apply cost  financial aid enrollment forms college relations news national recognition for the media alumni events make a gift tools webmail campus calendar mywc moodle online help desk columns careerlink back to top westminster college  hugh grant  close  menu home marketing  pr lectures  speeches hugh grant  pages under lectures  speeches  close marketing  pr westminster college news publications social media center for the media marketing tools live streaming contact us lectures  speeches symposium paul roberts hugh grant past ibm lecturers past green lecturers  ibm lecture overview  ibm lecture overview ibm lectureship in business and finance hjalma johnson green lecture speeches hugh grant hugh grant chairman president  ceo monsanto company hugh grant is chairman of the board president and chief executive officer of monsanto company monsanto is an agriculture company focused on applying innovation and technology to make its farmer customers more productive and profitable by offering products that help farmers produce food fiber and feed today monsanto has platforms in largeacre crops including corn cotton and oilseeds as well as smallacre crops including its seminis vegetableseed business monsantos established brands  including dekalb asgrow and stoneville seed  and its biotechnology products  including roundup ready soybeans corn and cotton bollgard insectprotected cotton and the yieldgard family of insectprotected corn  have established monsanto as a leader in the agricultural seedandtrait industry additionally roundup agricultural herbicides remain the worlds no  selling herbicides in addition to these core businesses mr grant is also responsible for the strategic planning and development of new growth platforms from monsantos researchanddevelopment investments in genomics biotechnology and other technologies applied to agricultural food and animal production systems prior to his appointment as president and ceo of monsanto in may  and chairman of the board in october  mr grant served three years as executive vice president and chief operating officer with overall responsibility for leading the operations and performance of the commercial seed chemistry and biotechnology traits businesses inclusive of sales and marketing information technology distribution and manufacturing worldwide mr grant joined the former monsanto company in  in scotland and spent the first  years of his career with monsantos agricultural business in a variety of european sales product development and management responsibilities in  he relocated to st louis as global strategy director of the agriculture division and was responsible for global management of the roundup herbicide franchise in  he was named monsantos managing director for the asiapacific region where he had responsibility for the companys agriculture nutrition and pharmaceutical businesses in southeast asia in  mr grant was named copresident of the companys agriculture division where he jointly oversaw global business operations and led the business and product strategy in this role he also formulated the longterm business strategy that led to an integrated product portfolio platform of chemistry seeds and biotechnology traits mr grant is a director of ppg industries inc and is a board member of the donald danforth plant science center and the biotechnology industry organization bio he is a member of the presidents advisory group of croplife international and a member of civic progress in st louis mr grant serves on the board of trustees of washington university and is an international advisory board member of scottish enterprise born in larkhall scotland mr grant earned a bachelors of science degree in agricultural zoology with honors at glasgow university he also earned a postgraduate degree in agriculture at edinburgh university and a masters of business administration at the international management centre in buckingham united kingdom monsanto company nyse mon is a leading global provider of technologybased solutions and agricultural products that improve farm productivity and food quality for more information on monsanto see wwwmonsantocom  request info  visit us  apply westminster college  westminster ave fulton mo  wcmo   email westminster quick links   about us who we are facts history outcomes student life campus map careers academics majors and minors signature programs registrar library catalog facultystaff directory bookstore admissions why westminster request info schedule a visit apply cost  financial aid enrollment forms college relations news national recognition for the media alumni events make a gift tools webmail campus calendar mywc moodle online help desk columns careerlink back to top hugh grant  haircut beard eyes weight measurements tattoos  style  muzul muzul muzul hugh grant hugh grant his beauty  look are characterized by his short hair ear length  crew cut hairstyle ladies love him for his strong jawline hugh grant the year old british actor from united kingdom was born on   you might know him from four weddings  a funeral want to look like hugh grant this handsome actor makes commercials for gendarme but actually uses issey miyakeface shapetypeoval read different face shapes with celebrity examplesbeard or mustachebeardlessdistinct featurestrong jawlinehair typewavyhair colordark browneye colorblueskin tonecomplexiontype ii fair skinskin typenormalhaircutdoes hugh grant smoke no smoking records read  most surprising celebrity smokers beauty products for hair  eyes etcfragrances  perfumesleau dissey  perfume by issey miyake pricepopular read  celebrity insecurities that would surprise you hugh grant body measurements  size  from feet to weight this cool talented actor wears mykita rolf figure  body typethinclothing stylealternativefavorite colorsblacktypical outfitsuitheight cmweight  celebrities with extreme weight issuesfeet sizebicepswaist sizebuste sizebutt size does hugh grant have tattoos currently no records of tattoos mustread the  most insane tattoos of celebritiesjackets  coatscoaches  coat by d